reviews.title: SUCKS, GLITCHES BAD!!!!!
reviews.comment: I\'ve got a new HTC sense, fully updated and clen of viruses. I tried this app, never changed how all average users search the web using Google. Then all of a sudden, the screen starts flashing between my desktop , this app, and the web pages/ tab previews. Took me forever, 3 hard resets to just get my cell to boot properly. Don\'t download!
reviews.author: sean lowery
